<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-slate-800">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          About Me
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Building the future of web, one pixel at a time
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Hello! I'm Saksham, a passionate web developer with a love for creating beautiful, 
          functional digital experiences. I specialize in modern web technologies and enjoy 
          building everything from sleek user interfaces to robust backend systems.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          My journey in web development has led me to work with cutting-edge technologies 
          like TypeScript, JavaScript, and Rust. I believe in writing clean, maintainable 
          code and creating user experiences that delight and inspire.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring new technologies, contributing to 
          open source projects, or working on my latest side project. I'm always excited 
          to take on new challenges and collaborate with like-minded developers.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 pt-4">
          <span class="bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Problem Solver</span>
          <span class="bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Creative Thinker</span>
          <span class="bg-green-500/20 text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Continuous Learner</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Quick Facts</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-slate-300">Based in India</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-slate-300">Full-stack Developer</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-pink-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-slate-300">Open Source Contributor</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full"></div>
                <span class="text-slate-300">Always Learning</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
